OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,FKen Wright was 16 when a school
OL,7,Fteacher told him he'd "never make it
OL,8,Fas a footballer".
OL,10,FIt was that reprimand which sent Ken
OL,11,Fon a lifelong journey of officiating.
OL,13,FSixty years on, the 77-year-old from
OL,14,FSwansea is still lacing his boots and
OL,15,Fputting the whistle to his mouth each
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,18,F"I refereed my first game when I was
OL,19,Fin school," Ken told ITV News.
