OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,F"My PE teacher told me straight, he
OL,7,Fsaid 'Wrighty, you'll never make it as
OL,8,Fa footballer so why don't you take up
OL,9,Frefereeing'.
OL,11,F"I can remember my first official game
OL,12,Fquite clearly. It was at Cefn Coed
OL,13,FHospital in Swansea and it was a
OL,14,Fhorrendous day, pouring down with
OL,15,Frain, I got drowned before I got to
OL,16,Fthe ground."
OL,18,F"I had a nightmare," Ken recalls.
