OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,FHe's been the man in the middle for
OL,7,FWelsh League games throughout his six
OL,8,Fdecades as a ref, while also taking
OL,9,Fthe whistle for West Wales Premier
OL,10,FLeague matches and university fixtures.
OL,12,FDuring the 1970s and 80s, Ken
OL,13,Fofficiated in games involving Arsenal
OL,14,Fat Highbury, Tottenham Hotspur at
OL,15,FWhite Heart Lane and Chelsea at
OL,16,FStanford Bridge.
OL,18,FHe was also appointed to Swansea City
OL,19,Fgames at the old Vetch Field against
OL,20,FEuropean heavyweights Paris Saint
OL,21,FGermain and Manchester United.
