OL,6,F"It was one of the best nights of my
OL,7,Fcareer," Ken said of being chosen as
OL,8,Fan assistant referee for the visit of
OL,9,FUnited.
OL,11,F"There were 28,000 fans inside the
OL,12,FVetch Field and as a local lad running
OL,13,Fthe line in front of the North Bank,
OL,14,Fthere were a lot of people who knew
OL,15,Fme. I had some abuse that night!
