OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,F"When I went to Arsenal it was a great
OL,7,Foccasion, but the best ground I have
OL,8,Fever been to is the old White Hart
OL,9,FLane when I refereed Tottenham
OL,10,FHotspur. It was a fantastic place from
OL,11,Fa referring point of view with great
OL,12,Ffacilities."
OL,14,FThis year marks Ken's 60th season as a
OL,15,Freferee and he is now bidding to be
OL,16,Frecognised as the world's longest-
OL,17,Fserving football referee.
