OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,FThe official Guinness World Record
OL,7,Fbelongs to Hungarian referee Csernyi
OL,8,FGeza who started officiating in 1950
OL,9,Fand retired in 2007, serving 57 years
OL,10,Fas a referee.
OL,12,FA referee from Cornwall, 83-year-old
OL,13,FBill Trethewey, made an application to
OL,14,Fbe recognised as the world's longest-
OL,15,Fserving referee last year. However,
OL,16,Fafter picking up his whistle in the
OL,17,Flate 1960's it was confirmed Bill's
OL,18,Fservice had only totalled 56 years,
OL,19,Fone short of the current record holder.
