OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,F"We have been so lucky to have Ken,"
OL,7,Fsaid Viv Nedin, Vice Chairman of the
OL,8,FSwansea Referee Society.
OL,10,F"Over the years Ken must have taken
OL,11,Fcharge of all the cup finals in the
OL,12,FSwansea Senior League on many
OL,13,Foccasions. I hope the record comes his
OL,14,Fway."
OL,16,FOn potentially being the referee with
OL,17,Fthe longest career in world football,
OL,18,FKen says: "It's a nice thought,
OL,19,Fpossibly my 60 years will surpass the
OL,20,Fcurrent record.
