OL,3,CCould this be the world's longest
OL,4,Cserving referee?
OL,6,F"I don't referee for the records, I
OL,7,Freferee for the love of the game and
OL,8,Fthe benefit of local football."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Guinness World
OL,11,FRecords said: "We would encourage Ken
OL,12,Fto make an application and we look
OL,13,Fforward to receiving the evidence for
OL,14,Four Records Management Team to review."
OL,16,FKen says he has no plans to retire
OL,17,Ffrom the game despite refereeing
OL,18,Fbefore England's Bobby Moore lifted
OL,19,Fthe World Cup and before the Scottish
OL,20,Fhand of Joe Jordan broke Welsh hearts
OL,21,Fduring World Cup qualifying.
